OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers soon dying out this evening.
OL,7,FIt will then be dry for a time before
OL,8,Ffurther showery outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Fspread in from the west later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,12,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,13,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,14,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,15,Fbecoming fewer later. Breezy,
OL,16,Fespecially around coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
